  "story": {
    "32415ae4-1cd4-48eb-9b00-3d026833d4de": {
      "v": "v1",
      "flow": {
        "raw": [
          {
            "id": "1",
            "cid": [
              "2-1",
              "2-2"
            ],
            "title": "",
            "content": "<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：连这种等级的残象都能创造出来&hellip;&hellip;但这可拦不住我们！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：果然，越靠近那尊雕像，出现的敌人也就越强大。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：二位，先前的战斗中有受伤吗？</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<div>\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2\">秧秧：我没有，倒是漂泊者&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n</div>\n</div>"
          },
          {
            "id": "2-1",
            "cid": [
              "3-1"
            ],
            "pid": [
              "1"
            ],
            "group": "2",
            "title": "没有。",
            "content": ""
          },
          {
            "id": "2-2",
            "cid": [
              "3-1"
            ],
            "pid": [
              "1"
            ],
            "group": "2",
            "title": "有一点。",
            "content": "",
            "delEdgeChildren": []
          },
          {
            "id": "3-1",
            "cid": [],
            "pid": [
              "2-1",
              "2-2"
            ],
            "group": "3",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：&hellip;&hellip;手伸过来一下。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：嗯&hellip;&hellip;果然，刚才的战斗还是给你造成了一些擦伤。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：我这有一些简单的草药，你先拿去敷上。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：之后的战斗只会越来越凶险，如果受伤，莫要逞强，一定要及时告知我。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：我们继续前进吧。</p>\n</div>"
          }
        ],
        "data": {},
        "structure": {
          "id": "1"
        },
        "individual": []
      },
      "title": "",
      "branch": "1",
      "content": "",
      "preLink": {
        "linkType": 1
      },
      "nextLink": {
