            "content": "<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：找机会从这里突围出去，在前方利用钩索甩掉后方残象！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">秧秧：鉴心！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">鉴心：此处残象来势汹汹，必须有人断后。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">鉴心：诸位，小道就护送到这里了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">鉴心：请各位，相信小道，继续前进吧。</p>\n</div>"
