        "raw": [
          {
            "id": "1",
            "cid": [],
            "title": "",
            "content": "<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：那轮&ldquo;月亮&rdquo;吸收了无冠者的频率，又创造出了另一头怪物。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：它是&ldquo;弯刀之役&rdquo;那时的&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">？？？：休想&hellip;&hellip;靠近&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：这是&hellip;&hellip;夜归军的剑术&hellip;&hellip;荒谬！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：小心它的远程攻击，暂避锋芒，注意躲避！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：漂泊者，你注意到了吗？</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：它的所有攻击都在有意避开身后的&ldquo;月亮&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;那轮&ldquo;月亮&rdquo;，可能才是敌人的核心。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：它的攻势弱下来了。这些攻击，交给我来打破！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：漂泊者，等待机会，攻击它的核心！</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">忌炎：&hellip;&hellip;连我的龙枪都复制过去了吗？</p>\n</div>"
          }
        ],
